This Project adds a plugin to include the following functionalities:

1. Include an additional column listing the currency attached to the mails by the sender specifing the importance of the Email relative to the sender

2. Include a Display Box Specifing the remaining Currency left with the user for the current day.

3. Include an additional input from user while sending the Email, to add the currency propotinal to the importance of the mail for them

4. Inclusion of additiona Header representing the currency attached to the mail, used in the 1.


